IV. Abilities & Unique Powers
Racial Ability (Corrupted): The Nymic Scream
Replaces "Command Animal"
Gaelen speaks a syllable of the Protonymic (True Name) of the local earth bones. He commands the environment to revert to the chaos of the Dawn Era.
Effect: Once per combat, as a Free Action, he screams. All natural terrain in the arena (trees, rocks, water) animates hostilely. Every character standing on natural ground must make a Hard (-4) Agility Check. On a failure, they are Grappled by the earth itself (roots, mud, stone hands) and take 4 Crushing Damage.
Unique Ability: The Paradise Mantle
Gaelen exists partially in Mankar Camoran's Paradise. He channels the immortality of the Ascended.
Effect: At the start of his turn, he regenerates 5 HP.
The Flaw: This regeneration is tied to the fluidity of his form. If he takes Cold/Frost Damage, his form solidifies ("freezes" in the static reality of Nirn), and the regeneration is disabled for his next turn. Likewise the burning effect will make him more liquid, doubling his healing for the duration of the effect.
Signature Spell: "Dawn's Breaking"
This is not a martial technique; it is a Unique Master Destruction Spell developed by the Mythic Dawn. It can be learned by a player if they recover his Grimoire.
School: Destruction (Master)
Cost: 8 FP
Casting Time: Major Action (Requires both hands)
Description: Gaelen channels pure Padomaic energy (Change/Chaos) into a single point in space, attempting to liquefy the laws of physics in that area.
Mechanical Effect:
Range: 60 feet.
Area: 10-foot radius cylinder (The Geyser).
Damage: 12 Fire Damage + 12 Magicka Damage (FP Drain).
